title: Rangers win AL West on final day, Hamels beat Angels 9-2
text:
> Sports Rangers win AL West on final day, Hamels beat Angels 9-2 Texas Rangers pitcher Yu Darvish, right, of Japan watches from the dugout with teammate Adrian Beltre during a baseball game against the Los Angeles Angels in Arlington, Texas, Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015. (AP Photo/LM Otero)
